  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售订单管理的流程图。起点是订单管理模块，用户付款后要进入一个判断节点，根据三种不同情况分流到后续处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "判断节点"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。付款动作是从第一个订单管理节点指向第二个节点吗？还是同一个模块内部的状态变化？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Get money"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是从A节点到B节点，标注为\"Get money\"，表示资金到账后进入待处理状态。这两个都是Retail_OrderManagement，但代表不同阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "Get money"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画了A到B的箭头，标注Get money。接下来B要连到判断节点C，这个判断是什么业务逻辑？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "判断节点C也是Retail_OrderManagement，根据订单来源分成三条分支：线上单、门店POS单、和第三方平台单。分别标注One、Two、Three。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "One",
        "Two",
        "Three"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "三条分支的终点分别是什么？Two是到Retail_PointOfSale对吧，那One和Three呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Two走门店收银系统Retail_PointOfSale。One和Three都回到Retail_OrderManagement，但是走不同的后续处理流程，所以分成D和F两个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。C分出三条带标注的线：One到D，Two到E（PointOfSale），Three到F。您看一下结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "One",
        "Two",
        "Three"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，B到C的箭头好像没标注？这个应该留空，表示无条件进入判断。还有确认下C的节点类型是菱形判断框吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，C是菱形判断节点，B到C确实没有标注，保持为空。还有其他需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "节点名称都确认是Retail_OrderManagement吗？除了E是Retail_PointOfSale。我怕之前说的和实际画的有出入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "F",
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "E",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误：A、B、C、D、F都是Retail_OrderManagement，只有E是Retail_PointOfSale。流程图已完成，从订单收款到三路分流的全链路都画好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
